      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This spell functions as @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.W0oa8tqHXAcWNaGT]{Hold Person}, except it can target any living creature.</p>\n<h2>@Compendium[sfrpg.spells.W0oa8tqHXAcWNaGT]{Hold Person}</h2>\n<p>The target becomes @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.NV4qXRDgb7zTNkW2]{Paralyzed} and freezes in place. It is aware and breathes normally but can&rsquo;t take any physical actions, even speech. A held creature can&rsquo;t cast spells. Each round on its turn, the target can spend a full action to attempt a new saving throw to end the effect. This does not provoke attacks of opportunity. A winged creature that is @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.NV4qXRDgb7zTNkW2]{Paralyzed} can&rsquo;t flap its wings and falls. A swimmer can&rsquo;t swim and may drown.</p>"
